location.fullValue: Taylor Plan, K. Hovnanian's® Four Seasons at Kent Island - Single Family

data.description: Beautiful 55 and older, single-level living with stunning features in the resort-like, amenity-rich community of Four Seasons at Kent Island. This beautiful home has it all! 10-foot ceilings, gourmet kitchen, beautiful hardwood flooring, 2 car garage with extra loft storage. Beautiful brick patio with fire pit overlooking a pond. Community amenities include 2 pools, club house for hosting events along the Chester River, gym, lawn maintenance, snow and trash removal and more! Welcome home!
